      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just so quiet here tonight. i've been staring at this screen for 10 hours and the only thing that \"interacts\" with me is a slack notification or an automated email. sometimes i feel like if i just stopped responding to everything... if i just disappeared from the chat windows and the inbox... it would be like i was never even here. like the world wouldn't even flicker.",
