      "content": "a \"permission to stop\"... i dont know. it sounds almost peaceful when you put it that way. but it feels wrong. like i'm just failing at life by wanting to check out. do you think it's actually wrong to want that? to just want to fade away because it's easier than being seen as nothing?",
